message.body: ok. need your suggestion. where would be a fun bar to go on a date with someone in minneapolis?
Bryant lake bowl, Barbette, galactic pizza, loring pasta bar, science museum (thats st paul though) or an art museum...?
Those are dinner sort of things though, what's the situation? And who's the guy?
We are just going out for drinks. he's good friends with emily robertson, but we met on okcupid before we realized.
Oh nice! I like those places... I'll send other ideas too, but Barbette is great! Very classy and eclectic. Kitty Kat club too, that's in dinky town
I love barbette too. maybe we'll go there. colin's girlfriend works there.
Or birch wood cafe or aster cafe :) there are my hits! Have fun, love!!!!
I miss you so much, martha. my body is feeling extremely warm and is feeling the distance..
Oh we've gone to the aster cafe!
I miss you!!!! God you'd be great in this program. I'm learning so much, we'll have so much fun working together I promise
